Wach moter ni kanyakla mar jo-Kristo man Sarde


1  “Ndik ni malaika mar kanyakla mar jo-Kristo man Sarde niya, ‘Weche mag Jal man gi Roho abiriyo mag Nyasaye, kod sulue abiriyo e magi:

“ ‘Ang’eyo timbeni duto, bende ang’eyo ni in gi nying’ ni ingima, to kata kamano isetho. 
2  Kuom mano, chiew mondo ijiw gima pod in-go, kapok otho chuth, nimar ayudo ni timbeni pod ok beyo ruok e nyim Nyasacha. 
3  

Omiyo par ane gima ne opuonji, kendo mane iwinjo. Make, kendo ilok chunyi iwe richoni. To ka ok ichiew, to abiro poyi ka jakuo, ka ok ing’eyo sa ma abiroe. 
4  Kata kamano, pod in gi ji manok e dala mar Sarde ma ok osechido lepgi. Gin giniwuoth koda gi lewni marachere, nikech mano ema owinjore kodgi. 
5  

Ng’at molocho bende norwakne lewni marachere, mana kaka girwako, kendo ok naruch nyinge oko ngang’ e kitap ngima, to anahul nyinge e nyim Wuora, kendo e nyim malaika mage. 
6  Ng’at man gi it to mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ni kanyalka mag jo-Kristo.’

Wach moter ni kanyakla mar jo-Kristo man Filadelfia


7  

“Ndik ni malaika mar kanyakla mar jo-Kristo man Filadelfia niya, ‘Magi e weche Jal maler kendo maradier, man gi rayaw mar Daudi. Ka oyawo gimoro, to onge ng’ama nyalo loro, kendo ka oloro gimoro, to onge ng’ama nyalo yawo. Owacho niya,


8  “ ‘Ang’eyo timbeni duto. Winji! Aseketo dhoot moyaw e nyimi, maonge ng’ama nyalo loro. Ang’eyo ni kata in gi teko matin kamano, to iserito wachna, kendo pok ikwedo nyinga. 
9  

To winji, nitie jomoko mag oganda jolemo mar Satan, maluongore ni jo-Yahudi, to ok gin jo-Yahudi, to giriambo ariamba. Abiro miyo gibiro, mi gipodhi e tiendi, kendo ging’e ni aheri. 
10  Ne amiyi chik ni mondo itim kinda, kendo iserito chiknano, omiyo an bende abiro riti e ndalo mar masira mabiro kwako piny ngima, mondo otemgo ji duto modak e piny. 
11  Abiro biro piyo, omiyo mak gima in-go matek, mondo kik ng’ato mayi osimboni. 
12  

To ng’at molocho anami bed siro e Hekalu mar Nyasacha, mi ok nochak owuog kanyo kendo nyaka chieng’. Anandik nying Nyasacha kuome, kod nying dala mar Nyasacha, ma en Jerusalem manyien, mabiro lor kaa e polo kuom Nyasacha. Nyinga maler bende nandik kuome. 
13  Ng’at man gi it to mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ni kanyakla mag jo-Kristo!’

Wach moter ni kanyakla mar jo-Kristo man Laodikia


14  

“Ndik ni malaika mar kanyakla mar jo-Kristo man Laodikia niya, ‘Jal miluongo ni Amin, ma en janeno migeno kendo maradier, kendo chuech duto mag Nyasaye noa kuome wacho kama:


15  “ ‘Ang’eyo timbeni duto. Ang’eyo ni ok ing’ich, bende ok iliet. To daber kibedo maliet kata mang’ich. 
16  To kaka koro indhemndhem, to ok iliet kata ok ing’ich, abiro ng’ogi oko! 
17  Iwacho ni in jamoko man gi mwandu mathoth, kendo onge gima ichando, to ikia ni in ng’at machandore moloyo. In ng’at modhier chuth ma jachan, Kendo in muofu bende in duk. 
18  To ang’adoni rieko ni mondo ing’iew kuoma dhahabu mopwodhi gi mach mondo inwang’ mwandu. Lewni marachere bende ing’iew kuoma irwakrigo mondo igeng’go dugi makeloni wichkuot. Yath bende ng’iew, iwirgo wang’i mondo inen. 
19  

Joma ahero ema akwero kendo akumo. Emomiyo ket chunyi mondo ilokri iwe richoni. 
20  Winji! Achung’ e dhoot kendo adwong’o. Ka ng’ato owinjo dwonda, mi oyawo dhoot, to anadonj ire, kendo anachiem kode, to en bende nochiem koda. 
21  To ng’at molocho anami bed koda e kom duong’na, mana kaka an bende ne alocho, mi abet kod Wuora e kom duong’ne. 
22  Ng’at man gi it to mondo owinj gima Roho wacho ni kanyakla mag jo-Kristo!’ ”

